{
  "texts": [
    "This results in a significant increase in labor and time costs for labeling the datasets created for a particular task.",
    "The success of the model training might also be significantly impacted by the datasets' annotation quality.",
    "Therefore, the creation of extensive and precisely labeled datasets has emerged as a critical issue for computer vision research.",
    "By using unsupervised learning approaches to extract hierarchical features, the requirement for a lot of labeled data may be reduced.",
    "Simultaneously, further research into how to construct effective and scalable parallel learning algorithms is imperative to accelerate the learning process."
  ]
}